          <title>Tanner Scott's $72 million, 4-year contract with Dodgers includes $21 million in deferred money</title>
          <description><![CDATA[LOS ANGELES (AP) — Reliever Tanner Scott's $72 million, four-year contract with the Los Angeles Dodgers includes $21 million in deferred salaries. Scott receives a $20 million signing bonus as part of the agreement announced Thursday, payable in four equal installments each Feb. 1 from 2025-28.]]></description>
